      <p>full of nasties. seriously. it has no harmful synthetic or petrochemicals, no sodium laureth sulfate (sles) and absolutely no ocean-life destroying microbeads. it's soap-free, alcohol-free, paraben-free and non-comedogenic so it won't clog up your pores. huzzah! and, as a natural preservative, the honey in face honey will keep your face wash fresh as a daisy for around 6 months, without any unpleasant preservatives.</p>
