      <img class="hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg" alt="face honey. ready to #facethehoney?" src="{{ 'it-wood.jpg' | asset_url }}">
    </div>    
  </div>

  <hr />

  <div class="row">  
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h2>#facethehoney</h2>
      <p>and treat yo skin. it's made right here in melbourne and only tested on very willing melbournians so you can rest assured not one single four legged friend was harmed in the making. not one single flippered, finned, wingged or walking creature for that matter! face honey is a gentle retreat from synthetic substances and smells delish to boot. for all skin everywhere, face honey is the sweetest wash around.</p>
